text: Erectile dysfunction (ED, also called impotence) is a condition where a man cannot have or keep the erection of the penis during sexual intercourse. Erectile dysfunction can be caused by issues such as death-grip syndrome or genital atrophy.Oertel, Wolfgang H., et al. "Reduced genital sensitivity in female patients with multiple system atrophy of parkinsonian type."
